foundry-cv (1.0.0) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Computer-vision toolkit: python3-opencv,
    libopencv-dev, gstreamer1.0-opencv, tesseract-ocr, libvips-tools.
    Atelier-only — opencv pulls libvtk9.5 (~275 MiB) which would prevent
    anvil from fitting on a 4 GB USB stick.

